Release Notes
This is a backtest from "Canais de Donchian-Teixeira Pirata" script, that can be found in my profile.

This backtest implements the strategy proposed by Hugo Teixeira.

It was written by myself for the "Bolsa de Valores Vapt Vupt" community.

Now updated to PineScript v4.

I hope you enjoy!
